					</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.4px; box-sizing: border-box;">第一卷上：创世记</span></strong>
					</p></section></section></section></section><p style=" margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;" class="_135editor"><br style="box-sizing: border-box;"/>
	</p><section style="padding: 0px 12px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; line-height: 1.9; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box;" class="_135editor"><p style=" margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">创世记讲述的是创造与祝福的故事。但是人类在领受神祝福的道路上遇到罪的重重拦阻，于是神与亚伯拉罕立约，要“通过他的选民让世界重新蒙福”<span style="color: #FFCA00; box-sizing: border-box;">[1]</span>。这就奠定了全书乃至整本圣经的基调：人败坏悖逆，神施行拯救。<span style="color: #FFCA00; box-sizing: border-box;">[2]</span><br style="box-sizing: border-box;"/>
		</p><p style=" margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br style="box-sizing: border-box;"/>
		</p><p style=" margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">关于创世记的体裁，学者提出了神话、考原故事、传统故事等不同说法。<span style="color: #FF8124; box-sizing: border-box;">《房角石注释：创世记》</span>的作者艾伦·洛斯认为，创世记既是神学著作，同时也真实呈现了历史事件。<span style="color: #FFCA00; box-sizing: border-box;">[3]</span>
		</p><p style=" margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br style="box-sizing: border-box;"/>
		</p><p style=" margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">关于创世记的文学结构，洛斯博士以希伯来文关键词toledoth（记述）为标记，将全书分为12个段落（见导言），而每个段落都是“整本书的缩影”，体现了“祝福和咒诅”的主题。<span style="color: #FFCA00; box-sizing: border-box;">[4]</span>
		</p><p style=" margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br style="box-sizing: border-box;"/>
		</p><p style=" margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;">摩西写下创世记，是要告诉以色列人他们选民身份的起源以及神要在他们身上成就的圣约应许。只要以色列人以信心和顺服来回应摩西的信息，就能和他们列祖一样，经历神的“拯救、供养和祝福”<span style="color: #FFCA00; box-sizing: border-box;">[5]</span>。而今日的我们要如何在这个因罪受咒诅的世界领受神的祝福呢？就让我们跟着洛斯博士一起到摩西脚前细细聆听吧！</p><p style=" margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br style="box-sizing: border-box;"/>
		</p><p style=" margin: 0px; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><br style="box-sizing: border-box;"/>
		</p></section><section style="margin: 0px 0%; text-align: left; justify-content: flex-start; display: flex; flex-flow: row nowrap; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;" class="_135editor"><section style="box-sizing:border-box;max-width: 100% !important;display: inline-block; width: 100%; vertical-align: top; padding: 20px; align-self: flex-start; flex: 0 0 auto; background-image: linear-gradient(to top, rgb(255, 243, 173) 0%, rgba(255, 243, 173, 0) 100%);"><section style="text-align: center; margin: 0px 0% 20px; line-height: 0; position: static; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing:border-box;max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; line-height: 0; width: 60%; height: auto;"><img class="raw-image" style="box-sizing:border-box;vertical-align: middle; width: 100%;" _width="100%" src="https://ehome.endao.co/book_image/detail/1669887987892.png" draggable="false" _src="https://img.xiumi.us/xmi/ua/3O1Ws/i/06486484a6d3c53eb584ac03bbe449d9-sz_1979970.png"/>
